net.hockeyapp.android.utils

Class HockeyLog

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.hockeyapp.android.utils.HockeyLog

  • public class HockeyLog
extends java.lang.Object

    Description

    Wrapper class for logging in the SDK as well as setting the desired log level for end users. Log levels correspond to those of android.util.Log.

      • getLogLevel

        public static int getLogLevel()
        Get the loglevel to find out how much data the HockeySDK spews into LogCat. The Default will be LOG_LEVEL.ERROR so only errors show up in LogCat.
        Returns:
        the log level

      • setLogLevel

        Set the log level to determine the amount of info the HockeySDK spews info into LogCat.
        Parameters:
        hockeyLogLevel - The log level for hockeySDK logging
